ingredientsDesc:
Reagents:
1.	< 5.0% Amikacin ANTISERUM (Sheep) in buffer containing protein as stabilizer and < 0.1% sodium azide as preservative (3 ml). Cap label “A”.
2.	< 0.1% Amikacin-fluorescein TRACER in buffer containing protein as stabilizer and < 0.1% sodium azide as preservative (3 ml). Cap label “T”.
3.	PRE-TREATMENT BUFFER containing a surfactant and < 0.1% sodium azide as preservative (3 ml). Cap label “B”.
Calibrator: human serum and < 0.1% sodium azide as preservative with amikacin.
